The error "cannot resolve symbol layoutBorder" is likely coming from this import statement in your code:

```java
import javafx.scene.layoutBorder;
```

This is an incorrect import. JavaFX doesn't have a class called `layoutBorder`. It should likely be:

```java
import javafx.scene.layout.Border;
```

Let's fix your imports:

```java:src/main/java/controllers/ListesHebergController.java
package controllers;

