## Note about Icon Images

In the FXML, I've referenced some icon images. You'll need to add these to your project at `src/main/resources/images/`:
- `home-icon.png` (for accommodation type)
- `user-icon.png` (for capacity)
- `price-icon.png` (for price)

If you don't have these icons, you can either:
1. Download free icons from sites like [Flaticon](https://www.flaticon.com/) or [Icons8](https://icons8.com/)
2. Or modify the FXML to use text instead by removing the ImageView elements

