- `@../images/location.png` - Location marker icon

Make sure to place these images in your resources folder at:
`src/main/resources/images/`

If you don't have these images, here are alternatives:
1. Download free icons from sites like [Flaticon](https://www.flaticon.com/) or [Icons8](https://icons8.com/)
2. Use built-in JavaFX shapes to create icons programmatically
3. Use Unicode symbols (but this won't look as nice)

